msgstr "Créer une composition"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1559
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Nom"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1562
msgid "My pattern"
msgstr "Ma composition"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1570
msgctxt "pattern (singular)"
msgid "Synced"
msgstr "Synchronisée"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1571
msgid "Sync this pattern across multiple locations."
msgstr "Synchroniser cette composition sur de multiples emplacements."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1590
msgid "Create"
msgstr "Créer"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1750
msgid "Manage patterns"
msgstr "Gérer les compositions"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1770
msgid "Welcome Guide"
msgstr "Prise en main"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1806
msgid ""
"A page reload is required for this change. Make sure your content is saved "
"before reloading."
msgstr ""
"Un rafraîchissement de la page est requis pour appliquer ce changement. "
"Assurez-vous d’avoir sauvegardé votre contenu avant de rafraîchir."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1821
msgid "Show & Reload Page"
msgstr "Afficher et rafraîchir la page"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1821
msgid "Hide & Reload Page"
msgstr "Masquer et rafraîchir la page"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1888
msgid "Custom fields"
msgstr "Champs personnalisés"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1915
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Avancé"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1921
msgid "Make the editor look like your theme."
msgstr "Fusionner l’apparence de l’éditeur avec celle de votre thème."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1922
msgid "Use theme styles"
msgstr "Utiliser les styles du thème"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1940
msgid "Fullscreen mode"
msgstr "Mode plein écran"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1941
msgid "Show and hide the admin user interface"
msgstr "Afficher et masquer l’interface d’administration des utilisateur·ice·s"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1990 wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2003
#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2059
msgid "Welcome to the Block Editor"
msgstr "Bienvenue dans l’éditeur de blocs"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:1991 wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2082
msgid "Get started"
msgstr "Premiers pas"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2004
msgid ""
"In this Editor, each paragraph, image, or video is presented as a distinct "
"“block” of content."
msgstr ""
"Dans l’éditeur de Retraceur, les paragraphes, images ou vidéos sont "
"présentés comme des blocs de contenu distincts."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2018
msgid "Customize each block"
msgstr "Personnaliser chaque bloc"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2019
msgid ""
"Each block comes with its own set of controls for changing things like "
"color, width, and alignment. These will show and hide automatically when you "
"have a block selected."
msgstr ""
"Chaque bloc propose ses propres réglages pour personnaliser les couleurs, "
"les tailles et alignements. Ces derniers seront automatiquement affichés ou "
"masqués suite à la sélection d’un bloc."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2033
msgid "Explore all blocks"
msgstr "Explorer tous les blocs"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2035
msgid ""
"All of the blocks available to you live in the block library. You’ll find it "
"wherever you see the <InserterIconImage /> icon."
msgstr ""
"Tous les blocs auxquels vous avez accès sont disponibles à partir de la "
"librairie des blocs. Vous la retrouverez partout ou vous verrez l’icône "
"d’insertion <InserterIconImage />."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2042
msgid "inserter"
msgstr "inséreur"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2060
msgid "A documentation will soon be available."
msgstr "Une documentation sera bientôt disponible."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2081 wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2094
msgid "Welcome to the template editor"
msgstr "Bienvenue dans l’éditeur de gabarits"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2095
msgid ""
"Templates help define the layout of the site. You can customize all aspects "
"of your posts and pages using blocks and patterns in this editor."
msgstr ""
"Les gabarits aident à la définition de la mise en page de votre site. Vous "
"pouvez personnaliser tous les aspects de vos publications en utilisant des "
"blocs ou des compositions dans cet éditeur."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2143
msgid "Exit fullscreen"
msgstr "Sortir du mode plein écran"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2143
msgid "Enter fullscreen"
msgstr "Entre dans le mode plein écran"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2150
msgid "Fullscreen off."
msgstr "Mode plein écran inactif."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2150
msgid "Fullscreen on."
msgstr "Mode plein écran allumé."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2519
msgid "Meta Boxes"
msgstr "Métadonnées"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2537 wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2543
msgid "Drag to resize"
msgstr "Étirer pour définir la taille"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2548
msgid "Use up and down arrow keys to resize the meta box pane."
msgstr ""
"Utiliser les touche flèche vers le haut ou le bas de votre clavier pour "
"redimensionner les panneaux liés aux métadonnées."

#. translators: %s: plugin name
#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2678
msgid "The \"%s\" plugin has encountered an error and cannot be rendered."
msgstr ""
"L’extension « %s » a rencontré une erreur et le contenu de ce bloc ne peut "
"être généré."

#. translators: %s: Title of the created post or template, e.g: "Hello world".
#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2705
msgid "\"%s\" successfully created."
msgstr "« %s » créé avec succès."

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2706
msgid "(no title)"
msgstr "(sans titre)"

#: wp-includes/js/dist/edit-post.js:2713
msgid "Edit"
msgstr "Modifier"
